00:28:26.140 --> 00:28:30.669
correct. So it's almost like a haiku, it's
a way of kind of containing, sort of mixing

00:28:30.669 --> 00:28:39.909
words and numbers together and there's something
rather sort of delightful about it. And if

00:28:39.909 --> 00:28:41.420
