00:38:12.090 --> 00:38:16.292
abacus, he sees the first one he just sees
it instantly as a shape on the abacus. He

00:38:16.292 --> 00:38:20.830
sees the next one and instantly he just adds
it. And he keeps on adding and he's like reading

00:38:20.830 --> 00:38:22.119
the printout at the end.

00:38:22.119 --> 00:38:30.040
And when I heard about I said, "Oh can I take,
