00:38:52.060 --> 00:38:59.530
do this about the sort of neurology of it
or the neuroscience of it, they say in Japan

00:38:59.530 --> 00:39:03.910
not that much research has been done on it
but they basically say, "Right brain normal

00:39:03.910 --> 00:39:10.781
maths, left brain," no "left brain normal
maths, right brain abacus." What they mean

00:39:10.781 --> 00:39:16.740
is that our left side of the brain, the left
hemisphere, tends to be used for linguistic

00:39:16.740 --> 00:39:21.440
programming, sort of language, numbers, counting,
all that kind of thing. And the right side

00:39:21.440 --> 00:39:28.140
of the brain is the visuospatial skills that
we have. So normally we use the left side

00:39:28.140 --> 00:39:32.220
of the brain to do maths but with the abacus
it's using the other side of the brain.

00:39:32.220 --> 00:39:36.900
