00:55:14.190 --> 00:55:20.630
ku is nine, so it's the nine nines and you
say it exactly as you do here. So we'll start

00:55:20.630 --> 00:55:27.619
one one is one, two ones is two, three ones
is three, but they sometimes like a number

00:55:27.619 --> 00:55:35.130
in Japanese one can be in it can be ichi,
two things. So the word that you use within

00:55:35.130 --> 00:55:39.520
the times tables is chosen to make it scan
